 4: Makes "Smileys" redundant ;)                            @{" Show me! " LINK "Images/smiley.pic/main"}

 5: Over @{fg mark}100 @{fg text}different graphics to bring IRC chat to life!  @{" Show me! " LINK "Images/graphics.pic/main"}

